OL,3,CPolice officer faces criminal probe as
OL,4,Cgrandmother and dog die following crash
OL,6,FA woman who died along with her dog
OL,7,Fafter a collision with a police car
OL,8,Fhas been named as grandmother Sharron
OL,9,FHall.
OL,11,FA police officer has been informed
OL,12,Fthey will be subject to a criminal
OL,13,Finvestigation and under internal
OL,14,Finvestigation for potential gross
OL,15,Fmisconduct, police watchdogs, the
OL,16,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,17,F(IOPC) said.
