OL,3,CPolice officer faces criminal probe as
OL,4,Cgrandmother and dog die following crash
OL,6,FAn initial IOPC investigation of the
OL,7,Ffatal incident has found mother-of-
OL,8,Ffour Ms Hall, 64, was driving a Suzuki
OL,9,FCelerio down Cleator Moor Road in
OL,10,FWhitehaven, Cumbria, around 7.50am on
OL,11,FSunday, January 19.
OL,13,FAt the same time, three officers were
OL,14,Fresponding to an emergency call and
OL,15,Ftravelling in separate vehicles.
OL,17,FThe second police vehicle, a Peugeot
OL,18,F308 estate, collided with Ms Hall's
OL,19,Fcar.
