OL,3,CPolice officer faces criminal probe as
OL,4,Cgrandmother and dog die following crash
OL,6,FMs Hall died in hospital the next day.
OL,7,FHer dog was in the car and was also
OL,8,Fkilled.
OL,10,FIn a tribute from Ms Hall's family,
OL,11,Fthey said: "She was a special, caring
OL,12,Fwoman who would give her help
OL,13,Fwillingly to anyone who asked for it.
OL,15,F"She worked at Howgill Family Centre
OL,16,Ffor over 20 years which she loved.
OL,18,F"She was a keen animal lover and you
OL,19,Fvery rarely saw her without her little
OL,20,Fdog Jack, who also sadly passed away
OL,21,Fin the collision.
