OL,6,F"She had a full and joyful life which
OL,7,Fwas full of love and she will be
OL,8,Fsorely missed by her family and
OL,9,Ffriends, especially by her four
OL,10,Fchildren, Andrew, Samantha, Mark and
OL,11,FTracy. She was an amazing mum, nanna,
OL,12,Fsister, aunt and friend."
OL,14,FThe IOPC said it was notified by
OL,15,FCumbria Police of the collision
OL,16,Fshortly after it happened and
OL,17,Finvestigators began gathering evidence.
