OL,3,CPolice officer faces criminal probe as
OL,4,Cgrandmother and dog die following crash
OL,6,FInitial accounts have been taken from
OL,7,Fthe police officers involved and
OL,8,Finvestigators are reviewing police
OL,9,Fvehicle dashcam footage along with
OL,10,Fbodyworn video.
OL,12,FThe IOPC said following initial
OL,13,Fassessments, an officer has been
OL,14,Finformed they will be the subject of a
OL,15,Fcriminal investigation.
OL,17,FThey have also been advised they are
OL,18,Funder investigation for potential
OL,19,Fgross misconduct.
