OL,6,FThe officer being informed of these
OL,7,Fallegations does not necessarily mean
OL,8,Fany proceedings will follow, the IOPC
OL,9,Fsaid, that will depend on the evidence
OL,10,Festablished from the investigation.
OL,12,FIOPC director of engagement Amanda
OL,13,FRowe said: "Our thoughts are with Ms
OL,14,FHall's family and friends, and to all
OL,15,Fthose affected by this tragic incident.
OL,17,F"We have been in contact with her
OL,18,Ffamily to explain our role, offer
OL,19,Fadvice and support, and to outline the
OL,20,Fnext steps of our independent
OL,21,Finvestigation.
