OL,6,F"There is a mandatory requirement for
OL,7,Fforces to refer to us incidents like
OL,8,Fthis, which result in death or serious
OL,9,Finjury, and our investigation will
OL,10,Fthoroughly examine the circumstances
OL,11,Fof the police involvement."
OL,13,FCumbria Police said: "It would not be
OL,14,Fappropriate to offer further comment
OL,15,Fas the matter is the subject of
OL,16,Finvestigation by the IOPC."
